{"tid":1377085,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登滲入警隊","createTime":"2019-07-28T12:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T04:57:29.000Z","uid":287461,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"95e68800d442764c4d068355d7c0e343a53bc776","tid":1377085,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:58:49.000Z","msg":"sorry標題有啲誇張。第一次出po。<br />\n<br />\np牌仔（其實係女）忽發奇想：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇可能搵多啲連登仔投考警隊，咁至少可以有啲自己手足係裡面裡應外合。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入到大學，愁緊做咩嘅，就考督察<br />\n入唔到大學，愁緊做咩嘅，就做散仔<br />\n警察咁撚高人工，唔通益班紅底/藍絲閪咩<br />\n<br />\n中共換緊我地血，警察都要換血。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「作為員警，不執行上級命令是有罪的，但打不準是無罪的。作為一個心智健全的人，此時此刻，你有把槍口抬高一釐米的主權，這是你應主動承擔的良心義務。在這個世界上，在法律之外還有良知。當法律和良知衝突時，良知是最高的行為準則。尊重生命，是一個放之四海而皆準的原則。」"},{"pid":"3261f013942730740af8883a913fd000339bd0c0","tid":1377085,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDT6T6zfZKY9%2BYzH6xvUt7sk%3D&h=73be4f7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n捍衛自由 不徹不散</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1374609/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1374609/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"31e40b951f2a0b73bbbd7605a40dd69a254052a8","tid":1377085,"uid":287461,"like"